 x^2 - (6k + 3 )x + 8k^2 = (x - a)(x -2a) = x^2 - 3ax + 2a^2 = 0
 (6k + 3) = 3a \ \ , \ \ 8k^2 = 2a^2 
2k + 1 = a \ \ , \ \ 4k^2 = a^2 
a = \pm 2k
2k + 1 = 2k \ \ , \ \ 2k + 1 = -2k 
1 = 0 \ \ \ (no \ solution) \ \ \ , \ \ k = - \frac{1}{4} 
k = - \frac{1}{4} \ \ , \ \ a = \frac{1}{2} 
